OL,3,CPainting of Cornish hero shot in
OL,4,CUkraine unveiled in front of his
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FA painting of a Cornish aid worker who
OL,8,Fwas unlawfully killed while helping
OL,9,Fhundreds of civilians flee a heavily
OL,10,Fbombed region in Ukraine was unveiled
OL,11,Fin Saltash last night.
OL,13,FChris Parry, born in Truro, was shot
OL,14,Fin the Soledar region in January 2023.
OL,15,FHe went to Ukraine at the start of the
OL,16,Fconflict to volunteer as a
OL,17,Fhumanitarian aid worker, and is
OL,18,Fcredited with helping more than 400
OL,19,Fpeople and animals to safety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
