PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780081925
OL,3,CPainting of Cornish hero shot in
OL,4,CUkraine unveiled in front of his
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FHe died at the age of 28 in January
OL,8,F2023, along with British colleague
OL,9,FAndrew Bagshaw. The pair went missing
OL,10,Fafter attempting a humanitarian
OL,11,Fevacuation, where there was intense
OL,12,Ffighting and shelling.
OL,14,FSaltash-based fine artist Louise
OL,15,FPasterfield has spent four years
OL,16,Fpainting nearly 300 portraits of
OL,17,FUkrainians affected by the war.
OL,19,FHer portrait of Chris was based on a
OL,20,Fphotograph given to her by his
OL,21,Fparents, Rob and Christine Parry.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
