PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780081925
OL,3,CPainting of Cornish hero shot in
OL,4,CUkraine unveiled in front of his
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FAt the opening of the Colour and
OL,8,FCourage exhibition at St Stephen's
OL,9,FChurch on the evening of Thursday 28
OL,10,FMay, Louise presented a print of the
OL,11,Fartwork to them.
OL,13,FRob Parry, Chris' Dad, said: "It's
OL,14,Fabsolutely stunning. I mean we
OL,15,Fcouldn't believe that she would take
OL,16,Fthe care and the trouble to do this
OL,17,Ffor us.
OL,19,F"It is an honour for us, and bringing
OL,20,FUkraine to the forefront again which
OL,21,Fis the main thing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
