OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780081925
OL,3,CPainting of Cornish hero shot in
OL,4,CUkraine unveiled in front of his
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FThe exhibition brings together 18
OL,8,Fwatercolour portraits from Louise's
OL,9,Fongoing Ukraine series. It's open to
OL,10,Fvisit until Sunday, 31 May.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
